@startuml SD-06_Report_Generation

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 17
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 300

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
    FontStyle plain
}
skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #333333
    ArrowThickness 1
    ArrowFontColor #000000
    ArrowFontSize 16
    LifeLineBorderColor #333333
    LifeLineBorderThickness 1
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    GroupBodyBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
    GroupBorderColor #888888
    GroupBorderThickness 1
    GroupHeaderFontColor #000000
    DividerBackgroundColor #E8E8E8
    DividerFontColor #000000
    DividerBorderColor #AAAAAA
    DividerBorderThickness 1
    ParticipantBorderThickness 1
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #999999
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}

actor       "User"           as User
participant "Web\nUI"        as UI
participant "Reports\nController" as Ctrl
participant "Reports\nService" as Svc
participant "PDF\nGen"       as PDF
database    "DB"             as DB
collections "File System"    as FS

== Generate Report ==

User -> UI  : Select format, click "Generate"
UI   -> Ctrl : POST /api/reports
Ctrl -> Svc  : generateReport(dto)

Svc  -> DB  : load Scan (must be COMPLETED),\nFindings, and AI Analysis
DB  --> Svc  : data

Svc  -> Svc : buildReportData()

alt PDF or HTML
    Svc -> PDF : generatePdf() / renderHtml()
    PDF --> Svc : Buffer / HTML string
else JSON
    Svc -> Svc : JSON.stringify()
end

Svc  -> FS  : writeFileSync()
Svc  -> DB  : save(Report, expires: 24h)
DB  --> Svc  : savedReport

Svc --> Ctrl : report record
Ctrl --> UI  : 201 Created
UI  --> User : Toast "Report generated"

== Download Report ==

User -> UI  : Click "Download"
UI   -> Ctrl : GET /api/reports/download/:id
Ctrl -> Svc  : downloadReport(id)

Svc  -> DB  : findOne(Report), check expiry
DB  --> Svc  : report

Svc  -> FS  : readFileSync(report.filePath)
FS  --> Svc  : buffer

Svc --> Ctrl : { buffer, filename }
Ctrl --> UI  : Attachment response
UI  --> User : File download starts

@enduml
